                     <interp inst="t18470201-480-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp> stealing 2 live tame rabbits, price 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18470201-name-210" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470201-name-210" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470201-name-210" type="surname" value="TWELLS"></interp>
